475300/extras/8395f1dc07c4f9bbdbddb194f75cda5f.mp4?t=1758321783\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Use quick thinking and detective skills to decode messages, crack safes, and outwit VILE operatives before they disappear. Every choice impacts your mission, so act fast!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CAPTURE VILE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475300/extras/782ea444078f6f0ae9389b7dd6015511.poster.avif?t=1758321783\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475300/extras/782ea444078f6f0ae9389b7dd6015511.webm?t=1758321783\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475300/extras/782ea444078f6f0ae9389b7dd6015511.mp4?t=1758321783\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Use clues, interviews, and the ACME CrimeNet Database to profile and identify VILE operatives. But remember, a warrant is essential before making any arrests! Will you crack the case and bring VILE to justice, or will they evade capture?</p>",
